description:
This plaque is located inside the Veteran Administration building if UAB, dedicated in 1967. At the time 
 of this building's construction, the following positions were filled:

Lyndon B. Johnson - U.S. President;
W. J. Driver - Administrator of Veteran Affairs;
Dr. H. M. Engle - Chief Medical Director;
Whitney Ashbridge - Assistant Administrator for Construction;
John B. Elliot - Resident Engineer;
Sherlock, Smith, and Adams, INC. - Architects and Engineers;
Walter W. Dean, INC. - General Contractor
